pandoc 
  to: html
  output-file: index.html
  standalone: true
  title-prefix: Ecological field research (GEO2-2439)
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  css:
    - styles.css
  toc: true
  toc-depth: 5
  
metadata
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: en
  editor: visual
  theme:
    light:
      - cosmo
      - theme-light.scss
    dark:
      - cosmo
      - theme-dark.scss
  code-copy: true
  code-summary: Show me the R code
  fig-cap-location: bottom
  title: Welcome to the tutorials of our Ecological field research course!
